{
  "texts": [
    "The Django application of the project is deployed on Google Run, a serverless computing platform, allowing it to scale based on demand without manual server management.",
    "The application's secret key is maintained in the Cloud Secret Manager for security measures, and all static files are stored in Cloud Storage.",
    "Furthermore, the Open Brain AI backend supports the Natural AI text and sound processing models.",
    "The backend design of Open Brain AI allows for scalability.",
    "Namely, the infrastructure supports automatic scaling depending on demand without server intervention."
  ]
}